              FIND
            .panel-body
              .find_icon
              .col-md-10.col-md-offset-1
                Search for and connect with locals to set up unique, customizable adventures
      .col-md-4
        %a{href: "/adventures/info"}
          .panel.panel-default
            .panel-heading
              HOST
            .panel-body
              .host_icon
              .small_text
              .col-md-10.col-md-offset-1
                Sell your expertise by leading like-minded travelers on the adventures you create
      .col-md-4        
        %a{href: "#", 'data-toggle' => "modal", 'data-target' => '#request_form_modal'}
          .panel.panel-default
            .panel-heading
              REQUEST
            .panel-body
